title: Auto to Text API
desc: An audio-to-text conversion API using FastAPI with the Whixper model from OpenAI. I've integrated Gmail login for sending transcribed text files, and I'm implementing FastAPI token authentication, Pedantic schema, and Alembic for database migration.

title: Social Media Content Creator
desc: This application is designed to empower users in generating content for multiple social media platforms, complete with customized images featuring their logo, website, and handle. Users can establish their brand identity before easily creating compelling content.

title: Flask Web (Portfolio)
desc: A dynamic website(resume) crafted through the Flask Framework, complemented by HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

title: Tweet app(Squib)
desc: Squib is a robust full-stack web application . Built with Django, Django Rest Framework, React.js, and styled with Tailwind CSS, Squib allows users to create, share, like, follow, unfollow, and retweet tweets.

title: House Price Prediction
desc: This is a machine learning model developed using supervised learning techniques, specifically the Random Forest Regression algorithm.

title: Resume
desc: Presenting my static online resume, meticulously crafted using a combination of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This resume is hosted on GitHub, making it easily accessible and shareable.

title: Clothes Store
desc: This innovative web application is built on a solid tech stack, featuring Next.js for front-end development, Medusa.js for e-commerce capabilities, and a reliable back-end powered by Node.js and PostgreSQL.
